_sText:
Its a remake/modification of the outstanding map alley_rush originally made by Nipper.

I always loved alley_rush, and when the only remake of it for CS:S was smaller and didnt have the house in it, 
that really bummed me out.
So i made a remake of it on my own, but its got other textures and stuff, cus i built it out of my memory.....
anyway, thanks Nipper for making alley_rush. It has given me many laughs :D
